QSteelWidget is a c++ Qt QWidget sublass that embed the Steel engine and offers methods to acces its API.

== engine ==
= mouse =

The middle button moves the current camera like in blender:
	- dragging the mouse while holding no key changes rotation
	- dragging the mouse while holding Shift translates the camera on a plan perpendicular to the camera axis
	- dragging the mouse while holding Ctrl zooms in and out
	ground, like in black & white)